{"tid":2253480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★機師去年擲近800萬入市東涌樓，恐被裁 蝕讓近220萬元急放！","createTime":"2020-10-22T07:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T04:08:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":18,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9b784651a20b51a767b1537f179b39d181117d37","tid":2253480,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:36:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">豪花百萬裝修 SSD滿一年即放盤<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201021/395680502784200704516097.jpeg/WtMDy4STZQxOJSCYayKilAHv_0QgeCfgicataonGrWo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201021%2F395680502784200704516097.jpeg%2FWtMDy4STZQxOJSCYayKilAHv_0QgeCfgicataonGrWo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=ac21b1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據該名消息人士透露，上述「四柴」機師於去年以約795萬元沽出東堤灣畔的兩房單位後，在同年11月以相同價錢795萬元，購入同區海堤灣畔1座高層A單位作自用，單位擁全海景，實用面積約582平方呎，並豪花140萬元裝修及添置傢俬。<br />\n<br />\n不過，近月該名機師預計自己將會被裁員，隨即向代理行查詢放盤事宜。據了解，該名機師得悉只要等到今年11月，持貨滿一年，其涉及的額外印花稅（SSD）稅項可由樓價的20%減至10%，便委託代理將其單位下月正式推出市場放售。<br />\n<br />\n由於市況欠佳，代理預料，該機師即使以買入價成功售出單位，計及10%SSD及已支出的140萬元裝修傢俬費，<span class=\"xx-large\">已涉近220萬元，相信單位「蝕硬」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/538575/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1-%E5%9B%9B%E6%9F%B4-%E6%A9%9F%E5%B8%AB%E6%81%90%E8%A2%AB%E8%A3%81-%E6%93%AC%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%94%BE%E5%94%AE%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%A4%E7%81%A3%E7%95%94%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F538575%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%259F%25B4-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2594%25AE%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25A4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%2595%2594%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=06e59f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/538575/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1-%E5%9B%9B%E6%9F%B4-%E6%A9%9F%E5%B8%AB%E6%81%90%E8%A2%AB%E8%A3%81-%E6%93%AC%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%94%BE%E5%94%AE%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%A4%E7%81%A3%E7%95%94%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF</a>"},{"pid":"906bda753ccb39156b5602eec6ea990e9c1d76c6","tid":2253480,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38eacb5cf39f37e56c840b588de46872ef8be3b","tid":2253480,"uid":137493,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce6dd800750d497c2931c780dc8e7ffb42be8c87","tid":2253480,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a38eacb5cf39f37e56c840b588de46872ef8be3b","tid":2253480,"uid":137493,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"房屋台變ifc台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a521b56df3aafa764561242e293ae0c1954fccb","tid":2253480,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7160c9aba98d12c74be13cd5af48e0dcad8e65de","tid":2253480,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"有剛需<br />\n正樓驚閪"},{"pid":"b6eb6cb31bc28999350588380422dc31dfeb65a6","tid":2253480,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東涌單日10宗國泰員工退租<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空（00293）宣布大裁員，觸發東涌租售市場機組人員「大逃亡」潮。昨單日錄至少10宗機組人員退租個案，一對慘被派大信封的國泰空姐，提前棄租僅租住了7個月的映灣園單位，惟業主最新僅以原本租值重新招租並提供議價，意味租金恐下調。<br />\n<br />\n同區的海堤灣畔亦有空姐被裁後劈穿底價以630萬元賣樓，較市價低3.1%。<br />\n<br />\n東涌租售市場大動盪，利嘉閣地產分行高級經理劉景駿表示，昨錄得至少10宗機組人員退租個案，主要集中映灣園，大部分租期仍處於死約階段，最短一個只承租4個多月便提出退租，但不少業主深明當前航空業艱難，「都唔使佢哋賠租」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A510%E5%AE%97%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%80%80%E7%A7%9F-202600071.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%259D%25B1%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%2597%25A510%25E5%25AE%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%2580%2580%25E7%25A7%259F-202600071.html&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=3080ec12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%9D%B1%E6%B6%8C%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A510%E5%AE%97%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E9%80%80%E7%A7%9F-202600071.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb854233c9419e3ec561b23cd793a442a7571554","tid":2253480,"uid":245849,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"800萬買東涌，佢真係信個市唔會跌"},{"pid":"79df3b891b3f50efed027186b5316f87fc864ceb","tid":2253480,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"東涌有牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0606d207c47da658da95121c0b10f0c1dbffb54","tid":2253480,